trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid"></xref> column that hosts <xref:System.Uri> elements in its cells.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid"> </xref> kolumn som är värd för <xref:System.Uri>element i celler.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: Use DataGridHyperlinkColumn to display data that contains a <xref:System.Uri>, such as an HTTP address or e-mail address.
trans-unit.target: Använda DataGridHyperlinkColumn för att visa data som innehåller en <xref:System.Uri>, till exempel en HTTP-adress eller e-postadress.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: The following illustration shows an example of a DataGridHyperlinkColumn.
trans-unit.target: Följande bild visar ett exempel på en DataGridHyperlinkColumn.

trans-unit.source: ![DataGridHyperlinkColumn with email addresses](~/add/media/wpf-hyperlinkcolumn.png "DataGridHyperlinkColumn with email addresses") > [!NOTE] > <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> navigation can only occur if either the direct or indirect parent of a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> is a navigation host.
trans-unit.target: ![DataGridHyperlinkColumn med e-postadresser](~/add/media/wpf-hyperlinkcolumn.png "DataGridHyperlinkColumn med e-postadresser") > [!NOTE] > <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>navigering kan bara inträffa om antingen direkt eller indirekt överordnade en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>är en värd för navigering.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>

trans-unit.source: Examples of navigation hosts include <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, or any browser that can host [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)], such as [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie6](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie6-md.md)] or later and Firefox 2.0 or later.
trans-unit.target: Exempel på navigering värdar är <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, eller webbläsare som kan vara värd för [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)], som [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie6](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie6-md.md)] eller senare och Firefox 2.0 eller senare.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the "Navigation Hosts" topic in [Navigation Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i avsnittet "Navigering värdar" i [Navigeringsöversikt](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: To populate the column, bind the column to the <xref:System.Uri> data by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill fylla i kolumnen binda kolumnen så att den <xref:System.Uri>data med hjälp av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A> </xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: To display hyperlink text that is different than the URI string, bind the text value to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn.ContentBinding%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: För att visa text i hyperlänken skiljer sig från URI-strängen, binda textvärdet för den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn.ContentBinding%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridHyperlinkColumn.ContentBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A> property is applied to the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> element created in the column.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>egenskapen tillämpas på den <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>eller <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>element som skapats i kolumnen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridBoundColumn.Binding%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A> for the element in each cell is the data item for the row the cell is in.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A>För elementet i varje cell är dataobjekt för rad cellen har.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, to set up the binding you only have to set the <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Därför för att ställa in bindningen behöver du bara ange <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Path%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Optionally, you can specify a <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName> if you want to convert the data.
trans-unit.target: Alternativt kan du ange en <xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Om du vill konvertera data.</xref:System.Windows.Data.Binding.Converter%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For more information about data binding, see [Data Binding (WPF)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om databindning finns [bindning (WPF)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > DataGridHyperlinkColumn creates a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> element in the non-editing mode and a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> element in the editing mode.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > DataGridHyperlinkColumn skapar en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>element i icke-redigering-läge och en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox>element i redigeringsläge.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>

trans-unit.source: If you want to display other types of data, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid> provides the following column types: |Column Type|Data Display| |-----------------|------------------| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>|Use to display Boolean data.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn>|Use to display enumeration data.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn>|Use to display text.| If you want to use other controls in your <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>, you can create your own column types by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn>.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill visa andra typer av data <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>ger följande kolumntyper: | Kolumntypen | Visning av data | |-----------------|------------------| | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn>| Använda för att visa booleska data. | | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn>| Använda för att visa uppräkningsdata. | | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn>| Använd för att visa text. | Om du vill använda andra kontroller i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>kan du skapa egna kolumntyper med hjälp av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTemplateColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridTextColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridComboBoxColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridCheckBoxColumn> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>
